opsgenie:index/alertPolicy:AlertPolicy.description:
Manages a Alert Policy within Opsgenie.

## Example Usage

<!--Start PulumiCodeChooser -->
```typescript
import * as pulumi from "@pulumi/pulumi";
import * as opsgenie from "@pulumi/opsgenie";

const test = new opsgenie.Team("test", {
    name: "example team",
    description: "This team deals with all the things",
});
const testAlertPolicy = new opsgenie.AlertPolicy("test", {
    filters: [{}],
    name: "example policy",
    teamId: test.id,
    policyDescription: "This is sample policy",
    message: "{{message}}",
    timeRestrictions: [{
        type: "weekday-and-time-of-day",
        restrictionList: [
            {
                endDay: "monday",
                endHour: 7,
                endMin: 0,
                startDay: "sunday",
                startHour: 21,
                startMin: 0,
            },
            {
                endDay: "tuesday",
                endHour: 7,
                endMin: 0,
                startDay: "monday",
                startHour: 22,
                startMin: 0,
            },
        ],
    }],
});
```
